summary: Skull Masks for the Nightingale Hood. Texture replacers.
descriptionHtml:
Skull Masks are two very quick textures replacers I made for the male Nightingale Hood. They change only the mask of the hood with a skull looking texture. You can use only one at time of course and replace the hood\'s original texture.

  To install simply unrar the file, choose mask 1 or 2 and copy the data folder to your game instalation folder ( where the tesv.exe is ) .

* The images I edit for making the texture replacers are not mine.
